        provided to third parties;
    (e) Use in any internal business operations of a Commercial Entity,
        including but not limited to internal tools, internal services,
        development workflows for commercial products, or productivity
        applications used in the course of business activity;
    (f) Use to provide consulting, contracting, or professional services
