3.2 Reverse Engineering Prohibition. You shall not, and shall not permit
any third party to, reverse engineer, decompile, disassemble, deobfuscate,
unpack, decompose, or otherwise attempt to derive, reconstruct, identify,
or discover:
    (a) The source code, object code, or underlying ideas, algorithms,
